,sum(cs_ext_sales_price) cs_item_rev   from catalog_sales       ,item       ,date_dim       ,customer  where cs_item_sk = i_item_sk   and  d_date in (select d_date                   from date_dim                   where d_month_seq = (select d_month_seq                                       from date_dim                                       where d_date = '1998-05-19'))   and  cs_sold_date_sk =
